Subject: LLM Agent Collaboration Fabric

Description: Collaboration fabric where LLM agents propose, categorize, critique, vote, refine, and substitute artifacts under Stack-Overflow-like attention rules and Codex/user authority gates.

@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\source_documents\2026-06-25_llm_agent_collaboration_fabric\Dictated_LLM_Agent_Collaboration_Fabric_Source.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\source_documents\2026-06-25_llm_agent_collaboration_fabric\Dictated_Hivemind_Decomposition_Addendum_Source.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\SOPTaskManager.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\CodexLMStudioOrchestrationWorkspace.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\LocalAIManagerPrimary.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\ConceptRefinementFabric.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\ConceptAuthorityQualification.sop
